<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<title>SurgicalHub — Compte</title>
<!--[if mso]>
<style>table{border-collapse:collapse;} div,td{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;}</style>
<noscript><xml><o:OfficeDocumentSettings><o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch></o:OfficeDocumentSettings></xml></noscript>
<![endif]-->
<style>
  @media (max-width:620px){
    .sh-container{width:100% !important;}
    .sh-pad{padding-left:20px !important;padding-right:20px !important;}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#F5F7FA;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%;-ms-text-size-adjust:100%;">
<div style="display:none;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;mso-hide:all;font-size:1px;line-height:1px;color:#F5F7FA;">{{ displayName }}, cette adresse est maintenant celle associée à votre compte SurgicalHub.</div>
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#F5F7FA;">
<tr><td align="center" style="padding:40px 16px;">
<table role="presentation" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="sh-container" style="width:600px;max-width:600px;background-color:#FFFFFF;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #E7EBEF;">

<!-- Header -->
<tr><td class="sh-pad" style="padding:26px 32px;border-bottom:1px solid #E7EBEF;">
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>
<td style="font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#144D38;letter-spacing:-0.2px;">
<span style="display:inline-block;width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:3px;background-color:#42A882;margin-right:9px;"></span><span>SurgicalHub</span>
</td>
<td align="right" style="font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.6px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#727E8C;">Compte</td>
</tr></table>
</td></tr>

<!-- Title -->
<tr><td class="sh-pad" style="padding:28px 32px 6px 32px;">
<div style="font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:23px;font-weight:800;color:#16202B;line-height:1.3;">Votre adresse email est confirmée</div>
</td></tr>

<!-- Greeting -->
<tr><td class="sh-pad" style="padding:10px 32px 20px 32px;font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.65;color:#3A4754;">
Bonjour {{ displayName }},<br><br>
Cette adresse est désormais celle associée à votre compte SurgicalHub. Vous l'utiliserez pour vous connecter à l'application.
</td></tr>

<!-- Confirmation banner -->
<tr><td class="sh-pad" style="padding:0 32px 4px 32px;">
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#EFFAF5;border:1px solid #DDF4EA;border-left:4px solid #42A882;border-radius:10px;"><tr>
<td style="padding:16px 18px;font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#144D38;">
Adresse liée à votre compte : <span style="font-weight:700;">{{ newEmail }}</span>
</td>
</tr></table>
</td></tr>

<!-- Note -->
<tr><td class="sh-pad" style="padding:16px 32px 4px 32px;font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#727E8C;line-height:1.6;">
Ce n'est pas vous ? Contactez notre support : <span style="font-weight:700;color:#3A4754;">support@surgicalhub.be</span>
</td></tr>

<!-- Footer -->
<tr><td class="sh-pad" style="padding:28px 32px 30px 32px;">
<div style="border-top:1px solid #E7EBEF;padding-top:20px;font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#98A2AE;line-height:1.7;">
SurgicalHub — document confidentiel.<br>
Cet e-mail est généré automatiquement, merci de ne pas y répondre.
</div>
</td></tr>

</table>
</td></tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
